  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00001",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "胡老头内嗽，上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00002",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "县令怜我缺断粮，吏胥不敢下村庄。年年麻麦收成足，半炷名香答上苍。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00003",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "小老儿，长安城外太平庄，胡老头的便是。今有大唐师父，要往西天印度雷音寺，求取大藏真经，唐家一十八路总管都到十里长亭，饯行发路。我家有一胖姑儿、王留儿，都去看盛会去了。我在家中，轧下粉饸饹，等他二人回来，大家好用。看，天到这般时候，还不见回来，待我出庄一望。",
      "text_length": 128
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00004",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "胖姑儿快走哇。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00005",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "王留儿快跑哇。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00006",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "咦，哈哈哈……看他二人，笑嘻嘻的来了。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00007",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "胖姑儿走哇。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00008",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "王留儿跑哇。咦，哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00009",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "胖姑跑上，王留随上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00010",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "豆叶黄",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "胖姑儿、王留儿走得来个偏急，王大、张三去得个偏迟。胖姑儿天生得这人意，姊弟相随，庄王儿离了官厅自到个这家里。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00011",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷，我们回来啦。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00012",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "哦，你们回来了。看的什么盛会，瞧的什么热闹，学来爷爷听啊。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00013",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷，我先说",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00014",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷，我先说。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00015",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷，我先说。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00016",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00017",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑",
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "我先说、我先说。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00018",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "王留儿，你姐姐大，还是让姐姐先说。胖姑儿，讲来，爷爷听啊。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00019",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00020",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "一缕儿麻",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑"
      ],
      "text": "不是俺胖姑儿心精细，只见那官人们簇拥着一个大擂捶。那擂捶上天生的有眼共眉，我只到瓠子头葫芦蒂，这个人儿也算得跷蹊。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00021",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "什么跷蹊，那是唐僧。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00022",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑",
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "什么唐僧不唐僧，原来是个和尚，我二人枉去这一遭哇。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00023",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "胡老头"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00024",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同一缕麻",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑",
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "恰便似不敢道的东西。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00025",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "胖姑",
        "王留"
      ],
      "text": "枉被旁人。咦，哈哈……",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904115_e00026",
      "play_id": "70904115",
      "scene_id": "70904115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
